    whatIs: "A Soulmate Birthday Match calculator analyzes two birth dates through four different compatibility lenses — Life Path Number harmony, Zodiac season affinity, biorhythm cycle alignment, and birth day number matching — to produce a composite soulmate score. Unlike a simple love calculator that just hashes two names, this tool applies multiple numerological and astrological frameworks, making the result feel more substantial and giving you more to explore. Each dimension contributes a sub-score, and the weighted average produces your overall soulmate rating.",
