    formula: "Life Path Score (40%): compatible groups → 85%, partial → 50%, none → 30%\nCompatible LP groups: (1,5,7), (2,4,8), (3,6,9)\n\nSeason Affinity (30%):\nSame month → 95%, Adjacent months → 80%, 2-3 months apart → 60%, Opposite → 40%\n\nBiorhythm Difference (30%): 100 − (|sum digits1 − sum digits2| × 0.5)\n\nOverall = LP×0.4 + Season×0.3 + Biorhythm×0.3\nClamped to 15-99%\n\nConnection Types:\n90%+ = Twin Flames 💫\n70-89% = Deep Soul Connection 💖\n50-69% = Promising Bond 💛\n30-49% = Learning Opportunity 🤍\n<30% = Not This Lifetime ⏳",
    useCases: ["Couples curious about their multi-dimensional birth date compatibility", "Dating app conversations: 'Let's check our soulmate score'", "Numerology enthusiasts comparing with Life Path compatibility alone", "Gift idea: frame a couple's soulmate score result as a fun keepsake", "Self-reflection: understanding why certain birth months might click with yours"],
    tips: ["The highest scores come from: same Life Path compatible group + birth months close together + similar birth date digit patterns. All three aligning is genuinely rare (~5% of random pairs get 85%+)", "Twin Flame (90%+) is intentionally very rare — it requires alignment across all dimensions. If you hit it with someone, save the screenshot!", "Biorhythm theory (the idea that physical/emotional/intellectual states follow fixed cycles from birth) is scientifically unproven but mathematically fun to compute", "This is entertainment, not relationship advice. A 25% soulmate score doesn't mean you should break up; a 95% doesn't mean you're destined. Real compatibility is built, not calculated"],
