    formula: "Life Path = reduce(sum of birth date digits) — single digit or Master Number (11,22,33)\ndailySeed = LP × 100 + today.day + today.month + today.year\n\nNumber i = ((dailySeed × (7i+3) + LP × (13i+5) + year × (i+1)) % max) + 1\nDuplicate check: if number already generated, increment index and rehash\n\nProperties:\n• Deterministic: same person + same day = same numbers\n• Unique: no duplicates within a set\n• Range: 1 to max (user-configurable)\n• Seed: numerological (LP) + temporal (date)",
    useCases: ["Picking lottery or raffle numbers with personal meaning (entertainment only!)", "Choosing numbers for games: fantasy sports draft order, board game selection", "Decision-making: 'Which restaurant on this list of 10 should we try?'", "Creative inspiration: using lucky numbers as constraints in art/design projects", "Daily ritual: generate your numbers every morning for a fun start to the day"],
    tips: ["Your lucky numbers change daily because the seed incorporates today's date. Come back each day for fresh numbers — or note which days gave you your favorite sets", "For lottery-style number picking, 6 numbers from 1-49 is the classic format. But you can generate anywhere from 1 to 20 numbers in any range up to 100", "The Life Path Number is the numerological 'heart' of this generator. If you don't know your Life Path, try our Numerology Calculator first", "Some people like to 'collect' their lucky numbers over time and look for patterns. While the math is deterministic, the human brain's pattern-recognition tendency makes this surprisingly fun"],
